{"text_id":178364,"tokens":["In","-","plane"," structure"," and"," ordering"," at"," liquid"," sodium"," surfaces"," and"," interfaces"," from"," ab"," initi","o"," molecular"," dynamics","."," ","\n\n","We"," employed"," ab"," initi","o"," molecular"," dynamics"," (","AIM","D",")"," simulations"," to"," investigate"," the"," in","-","plane"," structure"," and"," ordering"," at"," liquid"," sodium"," surfaces"," and"," interfaces","."," Our"," motivation"," lay"," in"," understanding"," the"," fundamental"," properties"," of"," metallic"," liquids",","," which"," remain"," a"," critical"," challenge"," in"," materials"," science","."," The"," AIM","D"," simulations"," were"," conducted"," using"," the"," Car","-","Par","rin","ello"," code",","," with"," tailored"," starting"," configurations"," to"," reproduce"," realistic"," surface"," geometries","."," We"," focused"," on"," the"," ","1","st"," and"," ","2","nd"," atomic"," layers"," of"," liquid"," sodium",","," which"," possess"," distinct"," structural"," and"," dynamical"," properties","."," Our"," results"," show"," that"," the"," in","-","plane"," structure"," of"," the"," ","1","st"," layer"," exhibits"," a"," pronounced"," ordering",","," with"," Na"," atoms"," arranged"," in"," a"," hexagonal"," lattice",","," while"," the"," ","2","nd"," layer"," exhibits"," a"," more"," disordered"," structure","."," In"," the"," vicinity"," of"," the"," surface",","," we"," observed"," the"," emergence"," of"," a"," stable",","," atomic","ally"," correlated"," layer",","," which"," we"," attribute"," to"," the"," unique"," electronic"," structure"," of"," sodium","."," Our"," findings"," provide"," new"," insight"," into"," the"," atomic","-","level"," behavior"," of"," liquid"," sodium"," surfaces"," and"," interfaces",","," with"," implications"," for"," understanding"," the"," surface","-","enhanced"," properties"," of"," this"," material","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}